 * Input shape:
 *   Arbitrary. Use the configuration `inputShape` when using this layer as the
 *   first layer in a model.
 *
 * Output shape:
 *   Same shape as the input.
 *
 * References:
 *   - [Zero-Bias Autoencoders and the Benefits of Co-Adapting
