 * ```js
 *
 * const model = tf.sequential();
 * model.add(tf.layers.cropping2D({cropping:[[2, 2], [2, 2]],
 *                                inputShape: [128, 128, 3]}));
 * //now output shape is [batch, 124, 124, 3]
 * ```
